---
// Terms of Service Page
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Terms of Service — TidySnap</title>
  <meta name="description" content="TidySnap terms of service">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --stone-50: #fafaf9;
      --stone-100: #f5f5f4;
      --stone-200: #e7e5e4;
      --stone-400: #a8a29e;
      --stone-600: #57534e;
      --stone-800: #1c1917;
      --emerald-600: #059669;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Outfit', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: var(--stone-50);
      color: var(--stone-800);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .heading { font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif; }
    .prose h2 {
      font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--stone-800);
    }
    .prose p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--stone-600); }
    .prose ul { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--stone-600); }
    .prose li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .prose strong { color: var(--stone-800); }
    .prose a { color: var(--emerald-600); text-decoration: underline; }
    .prose ol { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; color: var(--stone-600); counter-reset: list-counter; }
    .prose ol li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; list-style: none; counter-increment: list-counter; }
    .prose ol li::before { content: counter(list-counter) ". "; font-weight: 600; color: var(--stone-800); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header class="bg-white border-b border-stone-100 sticky top-0 z-50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-600 to-emerald-700 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold heading text-base">📸</div>
        <span class="text-lg font-bold heading text-stone-800">TidySnap</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-stone-500 hover:text-emerald-600 transition-colors">← Back</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 py-16">
    <div class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="heading text-3xl font-extrabold text-stone-800 mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm">Last updated: March 21, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose bg-white rounded-2xl border border-stone-100 p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm">

      <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p>By accessing or using TidySnap ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the Service.</p>

      <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
      <p>TidySnap provides an AI-powered desk organization service. Users upload photos of their desk, and our AI generates an annotated image with organization suggestions. The Service is provided "as is".</p>

      <h2>3. Account Registration</h2>
      <p>You may use TidySnap with or without an account. If you create an account, you agree to:</p>
