      <p>TidySnap offers the following subscription tiers:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Free Plan</strong> — Limited to 1 desk analysis per account</li>
        <li><strong>Lifetime Plan</strong> — One-time payment of $49 (early bird) or $99, granting unlimited access forever</li>
      </ul>
      <p>All payments are processed by <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stripe</a>. TidySnap does not store your payment card details. All payments are non-refundable unless required by applicable law.</p>
      <p>Early bird pricing of $49 is available for a limited time at our discretion. We reserve the right to change pricing at any time, but changes will not affect existing Lifetime Plan subscribers.</p>

      <h2>5. Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>You agree NOT to:</p>
