        <li>Attempt to reverse engineer, hack, or exploit the Service</li>
        <li>Use automated tools to spam the Service</li>
        <li>Resell or redistribute access to the Service</li>
        <li>Upload photos containing personally identifiable information of others without consent</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>TidySnap's name, logo, design, and original content are our property. The organization plans generated for you are for your personal use. You may not commercialize AI-generated outputs without explicit permission.</p>

      <h2>7. AI-Generated Content</h2>
      <p>Organization plans generated by TidySnap's AI are suggestions only. They do not constitute professional organization advice. Use your own judgment when following any recommendations.</p>

      <h2>8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, TidySnap is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service.</p>
      <p>In particular, we are not responsible for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Loss of data (your desk photos are not stored)</li>
        <li>Downtime or service interruptions</li>
        <li>AI analysis quality or accuracy</li>
        <li>Third-party service failures (Stripe, Google, Vercel)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>9. Service Availability</h2>
      <p>We strive to keep TidySnap available, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted access. We may modify, suspend, or discontinue the Service at any time with reasonable notice where practicable.</p>

      <h2>10. Termination</h2>
      <p>We may terminate or suspend your access to the Service immediately, without prior notice, for conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users, us, or third parties.</p>

      <h2>11. Privacy</h2>
      <p>Your use of the Service is also governed by our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>. By using the Service, you consent to our data practices as described therein. Desk photos you upload are <strong>not stored</strong> on our servers after analysis.</p>

      <h2>12. Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.</p>

      <h2>13. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by applicable law. If any provision of these Terms is found unenforceable, the remainder continues in effect.</p>

      <h2>14. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions about these Terms, contact us at:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:legal@tidysnap.homes">legal@tidysnap.homes</a></li>
        <li>Domain: tidysnap.homes</li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </main>

</body>
</html>
